  <body>
    <h1>Welcome in Gorill.IA prototype</h1>
    <p>As this project is still in its prototype phase, only words in french will be recorded here.</p>  
    <h2>Try to say a word !</h2>
    <p>Here are some keywords you can use to format the text:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>'Stop' or 'Go' will respectively 'stop' and 'start' the note taking.</li>
        <li>'phrase au centre' / 'phrase à droite' / 'phrase à gauche' will change the alignement of last sentence.</li>
        <li>'souligner phrase' / 'surligner phrase' / 'enlever décoration' change the decoration of the last sentence.</li>
        <li>'Titre' will make the last sentence a title and in the contrary 'paragraphe' will make a title back to a paragraph</li>
        <li>'effacer' will erase last sentence</li>
        <li>If you pronounce the word 'Important', the sentence in which it is will be in bold</li>
    </ul>
    <p>(If the prototype don't seem to work, try again by refreshing the page and verify you allowed the page to record you.)</p>
    <p><strong>Have Fun !</strong></p>
    
    
    
    <script src="sketch.js"></script>
    <script src="p5speech.js"></script>
    
